cs.IT, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.MM, cs.CL

This paper deals with wireless transmission and beamforming, which are topics related to information theory (cs.IT) and networking (cs.NI). The paper also presents an optimization problem and proposes an estimation method, which are topics related to systems and control (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper mentions the use of 3D channel models and array geometry optimization, which are topics related to multimedia (cs.MM) and computational linguistics (cs.CL), respectively.
